CustomField.description: The the name of the custom display setting associated with the incentive. This will be used when an existing incentive record is “Edited”. For a new record, the name will be passed as a URL parameter.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The the name of the custom display setting associated with the incentive. This will be used when an existing incentive record is “Edited”. For a new record, the name will be passed as a URL parameter.
CustomField.label: Custom Display Setting
